{"tid":2369000,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"細哨進軍樂壇　今年出8首新歌","createTime":"2021-01-16T16:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T02:37:19.000Z","uid":151196,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f21217d260309b9fc64387eacfe58c8b02f0e8ce","tid":2369000,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T16:49:01.000Z","msg":"巴西巨星朗拿甸奴度過失意嘅2020年後，新一年搵到新方向，就係進軍樂壇。英國《太陽報》報道，40歲嘅朗拿甸奴打算轉型做音樂人，並於今年推出8首歌曲，近日佢在一首MV客串演出，為進軍樂壇做準備。<br />\n<br />\n細哨去年嘅事迹不堪回首，年初入獄，在巴拉圭獄中與囚友打成一片，並捧走「監獄盃」，年中獲釋後又感染新冠肺炎，踏入新一年，細哨打算進軍樂壇。<br />\n<br />\n細哨MV演出：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3oUBMre\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3oUBMre&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=c066bd26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3oUBMre</a> <br />\n<br />\n細哨最近在一間自己同朋友設立嘅唱片公司MV中客串，影片中可見細哨被大批性感女郎圍繞，口味相當獨特，其後又在另一MV大晒球技，實行將音樂同足球結合。<br />\n<br />\n其實早在2016年，細哨曾推出自己嘅歌曲，為里約殘奧而創作，2017年再推出單曲《Sozinho》，意思為「孤獨」，2019年佢亦推出一首有政治色彩嘅歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n講到自己嘅音樂抱負，細哨話：「我希望我嘅音樂能夠觸動心靈，音樂與感情結合令我快樂。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newe/index.html?articleId=bkn-20210116230408581-0116_00882_001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffootball.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2Fnewe%2Findex.html%3FarticleId%3Dbkn-20210116230408581-0116_00882_001&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=c647112f\" target=\"_blank\">https://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newe/index.html?articleId=bkn-20210116230408581-0116_00882_001</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71e47d26d6948fabf82249236ea57b7a7e7b494","tid":2369000,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T17:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b452526b54480a01ef31a95a63c7158e8517af","tid":2369000,"uid":386601,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T17:11:09.000Z","msg":"乖啦！踢返波算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32fb79a5cf0e87c97969383564a4d9a770f2e19","tid":2369000,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"幾好啦﹐人地要挑戰下新野"},{"pid":"86545b40898650325332d203845cfc2b8f572689","tid":2369000,"uid":59283,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"幾時同莫文蔚合唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68502457b2e5a44b42dde4eb22c5a5e587b543aa","tid":2369000,"uid":189109,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PfGC4Xx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPfGC4Xx.jpg&h=00d5105e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以為係佢"},{"pid":"930ed4fc28267380ceee0c706ff041b7297a18f4","tid":2369000,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T00:13:26.000Z","msg":"個mv幾好波"},{"pid":"85343c0b3e3b0704ff171bcc7084a9385b0f8a0f","tid":2369000,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T00:15:27.000Z","msg":"第一首呼吸有害已經攞晒獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e611848c11e44ad6234839afb1ff82dc827b7c5","tid":2369000,"uid":3177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T00:23:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">少林功夫好嘢！ ～ 好好嘢</span>"},{"pid":"706ca21552f229bac17e19f27cf810a98f86f9f9","tid":2369000,"uid":1977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T00:35:08.000Z","msg":"森巴足球加唱歌跳舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23812da6e5c80bee01798169abee9f079ba8655","tid":2369000,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T02:30:34.000Z","msg":"現役depay 就真係出過歌<img src=\"/assets/f